BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:715bd0385b4facc24c02fb020479c193@mdh
DTSTAMP:20260717T121319Z
DTSTART:20260720T233000Z
DTEND:20260721T005000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Stick & Puck – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:<p>This clinic is designed for ages 12 and up. There is a Travel or Highschool level requirement for this clinic. This clinic is similar to Overspeed 2 in some of the content. However\, advanced game concepts using small area games will be more of an emphasis than in Overspeed 2.&nbsp\; Also\, game concepts like breakouts\, angling\, boardplay in defensive zone\, creating and taking away time and space will all be covered.&nbsp\; This clinic will also have a more technical approach to stickhandling and shooting concepts than other clinics. Learning how to protect and transfer the puck in traffic and learning various shooting techniques will be reinforced. There is also a dryland session that precedes each ice time.Mondays:</p>\n<p>Dryland 6:30pm/Ice 7:30-8:50pm<br />Thursdays: Dryland 6pm/Ice 7-7:50pm&nbsp\;</p>\n<p>*NO REFUNDS/CREDITS</p>\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
LOCATION:Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration
END:VEVENT
